high_descs: Move forward and then turn right to find the toaster.
Pick up the apple from the left side of the toaster.
Carry the apple and turn to the right and then the right again to find the microwave.
Place the apple in the microwave and turn it on. Open the microwave and take the apple out and shut the door.
Hold the apple and take a step to the left.
Place the apple on the front left side of the counter.
anns.task_desc: Heat an apple and place it on the counter.

high_descs: Go forward and to the right to face the counter where the toaster is.
Pick the apple up from the counter.
Go right and then right again to face the microwave.
Put the apple in the microwave and shut the door and then open the door and grab the apple.
Move to face the left side of the microwave cart.
Put the apple down on the cart.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated apple on a cart.

high_descs: Walk forward all the way to the counter then turn right and walk to the counter.
Pick up the apple that's in front of you.
Turn right and walk to the microwave that's in front of you to the right and stand in front of it so you can use it.
Warm the apple in the microwave and then get it back out and close the door.
Take a half step to your left.
Put the apple near the left corner of the surface the microwave is sitting on.
anns.task_desc: Put a microwaved apple on the counter.
